{
  "video_id": "g_3iLapiTCw",
  "title": "Vinay Venkatraman: Technology crafts for the digitally underserved",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Joseph Geni Reviewer: Morton Bast"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 12502.0,
      "end_time": 17787.0,
      "text": "Frugal Digital is essentially a small research group at C.I.D."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17787.0,
      "end_time": 19930.0,
      "text": "where we are looking to find"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 19930.0,
      "end_time": 24470.0,
      "text": "alternate visions of how to create a digitally inclusive society."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24470.0,
      "end_time": 26278.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s what we&#39;re after."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26278.0,
      "end_time": 28458.0,
      "text": "And we do this because we actually believe"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28458.0,
      "end_time": 31732.0,
      "text": "that silicon technology today is mostly about"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31732.0,
      "end_time": 33484.0,
      "text": "a culture of excess."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 33484.0,
      "end_time": 35657.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s about the fastest and the most efficient"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 35657.0,
      "end_time": 38860.0,
      "text": "and the most dazzling gadget you can have,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 38870.0,
      "end_time": 40985.0,
      "text": "while about two-thirds of the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 40985.0,
      "end_time": 44669.0,
      "text": "can hardly reach the most basic of this technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 44669.0,
      "end_time": 48251.0,
      "text": "to even address fundamental needs in life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 48252.0,
      "end_time": 50420.0,
      "text": "including health care, education"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 50420.0,
      "end_time": 54499.0,
      "text": "and all these kinds of very fundamental issues."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 54499.0,
      "end_time": 57744.0,
      "text": "So before I start, I want to talk about a little anecdote,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 57744.0,
      "end_time": 61766.0,
      "text": "a little story about a man I met once in Mumbai."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 61767.0,
      "end_time": 63954.0,
      "text": "So this man, his name is Sathi Shri."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 63954.0,
      "end_time": 66600.0,
      "text": "He is an outstanding person,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 66600.0,
      "end_time": 68202.0,
      "text": "because he&#39;s a small entrepreneur."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 68202.0,
      "end_time": 69944.0,
      "text": "He runs a little shop"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 69944.0,
      "end_time": 71947.0,
      "text": "in one of the back streets of Mumbai."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 71947.0,
      "end_time": 74995.0,
      "text": "He has this little 10-square-meter store,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 74995.0,
      "end_time": 77145.0,
      "text": "where so much is being done."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 77145.0,
      "end_time": 79500.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s incredible, because I couldn&#39;t believe my eyes"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 79500.0,
      "end_time": 81533.0,
      "text": "when I once just happened to bump into him."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 81533.0,
      "end_time": 83658.0,
      "text": "Basically, what he does is, he has all these services"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 83658.0,
      "end_time": 86411.0,
      "text": "for micro-payments and booking tickets"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 86411.0,
      "end_time": 89744.0,
      "text": "and all kinds of basic things that you would go online for,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 89744.0,
      "end_time": 91933.0,
      "text": "but he does it for people offline"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 91933.0,
      "end_time": 93930.0,
      "text": "and connects to the digital world."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 93930.0,
      "end_time": 95435.0,
      "text": "More importantly, he makes his money"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 95435.0,
      "end_time": 98280.0,
      "text": "by selling these mobile recharge coupons, you know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 98280.0,
      "end_time": 100303.0,
      "text": "for the prepaid subscriptions."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 100303.0,
      "end_time": 103544.0,
      "text": "But then, in the backside, he&#39;s got this little nook"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 103544.0,
      "end_time": 106116.0,
      "text": "with a few of his employees"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 106117.0,
      "end_time": 108701.0,
      "text": "where they can fix almost anything."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 108701.0,
      "end_time": 111958.0,
      "text": "Any cell phone, any gadget you can bring them, they can fix it."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 111959.0,
      "end_time": 115770.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s pretty incredible because I took my iPhone there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 115770.0,
      "end_time": 117246.0,
      "text": "and he was like, \"Yeah, do you want an upgrade?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 117246.0,
      "end_time": 119564.0,
      "text": "\"Yes.\" (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 119564.0,
      "end_time": 121503.0,
      "text": "I was a bit skeptical, but then, I decided"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 121504.0,
      "end_time": 126137.0,
      "text": "to give him a Nokia instead. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 126137.0,
      "end_time": 131352.0,
      "text": "But what I was amazed about is this reverse engineering"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 131352.0,
      "end_time": 136304.0,
      "text": "and know-how that&#39;s built into this little two meters of space."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 136304.0,
      "end_time": 138895.0,
      "text": "They have figured out everything that&#39;s required"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 138895.0,
      "end_time": 140921.0,
      "text": "to dismantle, take things apart,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 140921.0,
      "end_time": 143880.0,
      "text": "rewrite the circuitry, re-flash the firmware,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 143880.0,
      "end_time": 145847.0,
      "text": "do whatever you want to with the phone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 145847.0,
      "end_time": 148416.0,
      "text": "and they can fix anything so quickly."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 148416.0,
      "end_time": 150416.0,
      "text": "You can hand over a phone this morning"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 150416.0,
      "end_time": 152335.0,
      "text": "and you can go pick it up after lunch,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 152336.0,
      "end_time": 154256.0,
      "text": "and it was quite incredible."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 154256.0,
      "end_time": 155827.0,
      "text": "But then we were wondering whether this is"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 155827.0,
      "end_time": 158369.0,
      "text": "a local phenomenon, or is truly global?"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 158369.0,
      "end_time": 160619.0,
      "text": "And, over time, we started understanding"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 160619.0,
      "end_time": 162338.0,
      "text": "and systematically researching"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 162338.0,
      "end_time": 164454.0,
      "text": "what this tinkering ecosystem is about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 164454.0,
      "end_time": 166590.0,
      "text": "because that is something that&#39;s happening"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 166590.0,
      "end_time": 168910.0,
      "text": "not just in one street corner in Mumbai."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 168910.0,
      "end_time": 171205.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s actually happening in all parts of the country."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 171205.0,
      "end_time": 173466.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s even happening in Africa, like, for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 173466.0,
      "end_time": 175513.0,
      "text": "in Cape Town we did extensive research on this."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 175513.0,
      "end_time": 178708.0,
      "text": "Even here in Doha I found this little nook"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 178708.0,
      "end_time": 181595.0,
      "text": "where you can get alarm clocks and watches fixed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 181595.0,
      "end_time": 184796.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s a lot of tiny little parts. It&#39;s not easy."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 184796.0,
      "end_time": 186909.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ve got to try it on your own to believe it."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 186909.0,
      "end_time": 188463.0,
      "text": "But what fuels this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 188463.0,
      "end_time": 191971.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s this entire ecosystem of low-cost parts"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 191971.0,
      "end_time": 195277.0,
      "text": "and supplies that are produced all over the world, literally,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 195277.0,
      "end_time": 199420.0,
      "text": "and then redistributed to basically service this industry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 199430.0,
      "end_time": 201214.0,
      "text": "and you can even buy salvaged parts."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 201214.0,
      "end_time": 203370.0,
      "text": "Basically, you don&#39;t have to necessarily buy"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 203370.0,
      "end_time": 205833.0,
      "text": "brand new things. You have condemned computers"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 205833.0,
      "end_time": 207140.0,
      "text": "that are stripped apart,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 207140.0,
      "end_time": 208709.0,
      "text": "and you can buy salvaged components"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 208710.0,
      "end_time": 212531.0,
      "text": "and things that you can reassemble in a new configuration."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 212531.0,
      "end_time": 216120.0,
      "text": "But what does this new, sort of, approach give us?"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 216120.0,
      "end_time": 217932.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s the real question, because this is something"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 217932.0,
      "end_time": 220156.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s been there, part of every society"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 220157.0,
      "end_time": 222523.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s deprived of enough resources."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 222523.0,
      "end_time": 224420.0,
      "text": "But there&#39;s an interesting paradigm."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 224420.0,
      "end_time": 225911.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s the traditional crafts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 225912.0,
      "end_time": 227915.0,
      "text": "and then there&#39;s the technology crafts."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 227915.0,
      "end_time": 230123.0,
      "text": "We call it the technology crafts because these are emerging."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 230123.0,
      "end_time": 232195.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re not something that&#39;s been established."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 232195.0,
      "end_time": 234862.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not something that&#39;s institutionalized."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 234862.0,
      "end_time": 236632.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not taught in universities."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 236633.0,
      "end_time": 238356.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s taught [by] word of mouth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 238356.0,
      "end_time": 240265.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s an informal education system around this."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 240265.0,
      "end_time": 243660.0,
      "text": "So we said, \"What can we get out of this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 243670.0,
      "end_time": 245801.0,
      "text": "You know, like, what are the key values that we can get out of this?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 245801.0,
      "end_time": 248146.0,
      "text": "The main thing is a fix-it-locally culture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 248146.0,
      "end_time": 250486.0,
      "text": "which is fantastic because it means that your product"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 250486.0,
      "end_time": 252530.0,
      "text": "or your service doesn&#39;t have to go through"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 252531.0,
      "end_time": 255139.0,
      "text": "a huge bureaucratic system to get it fixed."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 255139.0,
      "end_time": 258218.0,
      "text": "It also affords us cheap fabrication, which is fantastic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 258218.00000000003,
      "end_time": 260250.00000000003,
      "text": "so it means that you can do a lot more with it."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 260250.0,
      "end_time": 262564.0,
      "text": "And then, the most important thing is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 262564.0,
      "end_time": 264940.0,
      "text": "it gives us large math for low cost."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 264940.0,
      "end_time": 267269.0,
      "text": "So it means that you can actually embed"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 267269.0,
      "end_time": 270794.0,
      "text": "pretty clever algorithms and lots of other kinds"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 270794.0,
      "end_time": 274452.0,
      "text": "of extendable ideas into really simple devices."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 274452.0,
      "end_time": 279260.0,
      "text": "So, what we call this is a silicon cottage industry."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 279260.0,
      "end_time": 282206.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s basically what was the system or the paradigm"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 282206.0,
      "end_time": 284670.0,
      "text": "before the industrial revolution is now re-happening"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 284670.0,
      "end_time": 287678.0,
      "text": "in a whole new way in small digital shops"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 287678.0,
      "end_time": 290759.0,
      "text": "across the planet in most developing countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 290759.0,
      "end_time": 294893.0,
      "text": "So, we kind of toyed around with this idea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 294893.0,
      "end_time": 296570.0,
      "text": "and we said, \"What can we do with this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 296571.0,
      "end_time": 299990.0,
      "text": "Can we make a little product or a service out of it?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 299990.0,
      "end_time": 301519.0,
      "text": "So one of the first things we did is this thing called"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 301519.0,
      "end_time": 303915.0,
      "text": "a multimedia platform. We call it a lunch box."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 303915.0,
      "end_time": 306666.0,
      "text": "Basically one of the contexts that we studied was"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 306666.0,
      "end_time": 310153.0,
      "text": "schools in very remote parts of India."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 310153.0,
      "end_time": 313412.0,
      "text": "So there is this amazing concept called the one-teacher school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 313412.0,
      "end_time": 316114.0,
      "text": "which is basically a single teacher who is a multitasker"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 316114.0,
      "end_time": 318590.0,
      "text": "who teaches this amazing little social setting."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 318591.0,
      "end_time": 320128.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s an informal school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 320128.0,
      "end_time": 322287.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s really about holistic education."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 322287.0,
      "end_time": 323525.0,
      "text": "The only thing that they don&#39;t have"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 323525.0,
      "end_time": 325919.0,
      "text": "is access to resources. They don&#39;t even have a textbook"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 325919.0,
      "end_time": 328746.0,
      "text": "sometimes, and they don&#39;t even have a proper curriculum."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 328746.0,
      "end_time": 332250.0,
      "text": "So we said, \"What can we do to empower this teacher"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 332250.0,
      "end_time": 335620.0,
      "text": "to do more?\" How to access the digital world?"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 335620.0,
      "end_time": 337624.0,
      "text": "Instead of being the sole guardian of information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 337624.0,
      "end_time": 340280.0,
      "text": "be a facilitator to all this information."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 340280.0,
      "end_time": 343412.0,
      "text": "So we said, \"What are the steps required to empower the teacher?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 343412.0,
      "end_time": 346660.0,
      "text": "How do you make this teacher into a digital gateway,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 346670.0,
      "end_time": 348599.0,
      "text": "and how do you design an inexpensive multimedia platform"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 348599.0,
      "end_time": 351591.0,
      "text": "that can be constructed locally and serviced locally?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 351591.0,
      "end_time": 353934.0,
      "text": "So we walked around."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 353934.0,
      "end_time": 356224.0,
      "text": "We went and scavenged the nearby markets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 356224.0,
      "end_time": 360245.0,
      "text": "and we tried to understand, \"What can we pick up that will make this happen?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 360245.0,
      "end_time": 362772.0,
      "text": "So the thing that we got"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 362772.0,
      "end_time": 365979.0,
      "text": "was a little mobile phone with a little pico projector"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 365979.0,
      "end_time": 368316.0,
      "text": "that comes for about 60 dollars."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 368316.0,
      "end_time": 370772.0,
      "text": "We went a bought a flashlight with a very big battery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 370772.0,
      "end_time": 372562.0,
      "text": "and a bunch of small speakers."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 372562.0,
      "end_time": 374860.0,
      "text": "So essentially, the mobile phone gives us"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 374860.0,
      "end_time": 376784.0,
      "text": "a connected multimedia platform."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 376784.0,
      "end_time": 380269.0,
      "text": "It allows us to get online and allows us to load up files"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 380269.0,
      "end_time": 382620.0,
      "text": "of different formats and play them."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 382620.0,
      "end_time": 385646.0,
      "text": "The flashlight gives us this really intense, bright L.E.D.,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 385646.0,
      "end_time": 388637.0,
      "text": "and six hours worth of rechargeable battery pack,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 388637.0,
      "end_time": 390853.0,
      "text": "and the lunch box is a nice little package"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 390853.0,
      "end_time": 392900.0,
      "text": "in which you can put everything inside,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 392900.0,
      "end_time": 394462.0,
      "text": "and a bunch of mini speakers to sort of"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 394463.0,
      "end_time": 395881.0,
      "text": "amplify the sound large enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 395881.0,
      "end_time": 399419.0,
      "text": "Believe me, those little classrooms are really noisy."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 399420.0,
      "end_time": 402130.0,
      "text": "They are kids who scream at the top of their voices,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 402130.0,
      "end_time": 403673.0,
      "text": "and you really have to get above that."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 403673.0,
      "end_time": 406394.0,
      "text": "And we took it back to this little tinkering setup"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 406394.0,
      "end_time": 408484.0,
      "text": "of a mobile phone repair shop,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 408484.0,
      "end_time": 409912.0,
      "text": "and then the magic happens."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 409912.0,
      "end_time": 411292.0,
      "text": "We dismantle the whole thing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 411293.0,
      "end_time": 413650.0,
      "text": "we reassemble it in a new configuration,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 413650.0,
      "end_time": 415828.0,
      "text": "and we do this hardware mashup,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 415828.0,
      "end_time": 418436.0,
      "text": "systematically training the guy how to do this."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 418437.0,
      "end_time": 421892.0,
      "text": "Out comes this, a little lunch box -- form factor."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 421892.0,
      "end_time": 428718.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 428718.0,
      "end_time": 431736.0,
      "text": "And we systematically field tested,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 431736.0,
      "end_time": 434104.0,
      "text": "because in the field testing we learned some"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 434104.0,
      "end_time": 436621.0,
      "text": "important lessons, and we went through many iterations."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 436621.0,
      "end_time": 439316.0,
      "text": "One of the key issues was battery consumption and charging."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 439316.0,
      "end_time": 443294.0,
      "text": "Luminosity was an issue, when you have too much bright sunlight outside."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 443294.0,
      "end_time": 445846.0,
      "text": "Often the roofs are broken, so you don&#39;t have enough"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 445846.0,
      "end_time": 448974.0,
      "text": "darkness in the classroom to do these things."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 448974.0,
      "end_time": 451816.0,
      "text": "We extended this idea. We tested it many times over,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 451816.0,
      "end_time": 454393.0,
      "text": "and the next version we came up with was a box"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 454394.0,
      "end_time": 456774.0,
      "text": "that kind of could trickle charge on solar energy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 456774.0,
      "end_time": 459573.0,
      "text": "but most importantly connect to a car battery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 459573.0,
      "end_time": 462567.0,
      "text": "because a car battery is a ubiquitous source of power"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 462567.0,
      "end_time": 464774.0,
      "text": "in places where there&#39;s not enough electricity"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 464774.0,
      "end_time": 466734.0,
      "text": "or erratic electricity."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 466734.0,
      "end_time": 468703.0,
      "text": "And the other key thing that we did was"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 468703.0,
      "end_time": 471164.0,
      "text": "make this box run off a USB key, because we realized"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 471165.0,
      "end_time": 474519.0,
      "text": "that even though there was GPRS and all that on paper,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 474519.0,
      "end_time": 477940.0,
      "text": "at least, in theory, it was much more efficient"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 477940.0,
      "end_time": 480984.0,
      "text": "to send the data on a little USB key by surface mail."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 480984.0,
      "end_time": 482823.0,
      "text": "It might take a few days to get there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 482824.0,
      "end_time": 485198.0,
      "text": "but at least it gets there in high definition"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 485198.0,
      "end_time": 487412.0,
      "text": "and in a reliable quality."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 487413.0,
      "end_time": 489695.0,
      "text": "So we made this box, and we tested it again"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 489695.0,
      "end_time": 491230.0,
      "text": "and again and again, and we&#39;re going through"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 491230.0,
      "end_time": 492779.0,
      "text": "multiple iterations to do these things."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 492779.0,
      "end_time": 495748.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s not limited to just education."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 495748.0,
      "end_time": 497614.0,
      "text": "This kind of a technique or metrology"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 497614.0,
      "end_time": 499626.0,
      "text": "can actually be applied to other kinds of areas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 499626.0,
      "end_time": 501534.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m going to tell you one more little story."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 501534.0,
      "end_time": 503989.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s about this little device called a medi-meter."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 503989.0,
      "end_time": 507356.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s basically a little health care screening tool that we developed."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 507356.0,
      "end_time": 510683.0,
      "text": "In India, there is a context of these amazing people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 510683.0,
      "end_time": 512962.0,
      "text": "the health care workers called ASHA workers."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 512962.0,
      "end_time": 515379.0,
      "text": "They are essentially foot soldiers for the health care system"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 515379.0,
      "end_time": 517763.0,
      "text": "who live in the local community and are trained"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 517763.00000000006,
      "end_time": 520331.00000000006,
      "text": "with basic tools and basic concepts of health care,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 520331.0,
      "end_time": 524920.0,
      "text": "and the main purpose is basically to inform people"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 524920.0,
      "end_time": 527626.0,
      "text": "to basically, how to lead a better life, but also"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 527626.0,
      "end_time": 530853.0,
      "text": "to divert or sort of make recommendations"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 530854.0,
      "end_time": 533528.0,
      "text": "of what kind of health care should they approach?"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 533528.0,
      "end_time": 536240.0,
      "text": "They are basically referral services, essentially."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 536240.0,
      "end_time": 538548.0,
      "text": "But the problem with that is that we realized"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 538548.0,
      "end_time": 542738.0,
      "text": "after a bunch of research that they are amazing"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 542738.0,
      "end_time": 545218.0,
      "text": "at referring people to the nearest clinic"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 545218.0,
      "end_time": 548910.0,
      "text": "or the public health care system, but what happens at the"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 548910.0,
      "end_time": 552169.0,
      "text": "public health care system is this: these incredibly long lines"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 552169.0,
      "end_time": 554978.0,
      "text": "and too many people who overload the system"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 554979.0,
      "end_time": 557545.0,
      "text": "simply because there&#39;s not enough doctors and facilities"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 557545.0,
      "end_time": 559747.0,
      "text": "for the population that&#39;s being referred."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 559747.0,
      "end_time": 561866.0,
      "text": "So everything from a common cold"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 561866.0,
      "end_time": 564526.0,
      "text": "to a serious case of malaria gets almost the same"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 564526.0,
      "end_time": 567569.0,
      "text": "level of attention, and there&#39;s no priorities."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 567570.0,
      "end_time": 569641.0,
      "text": "So we said, \"Come on, there&#39;s got to be a better way"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 569641.0,
      "end_time": 571442.0,
      "text": "of doing this for sure.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 571442.0,
      "end_time": 574190.0,
      "text": "So we said, \"What can we do with the ASHA worker"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 574190.0,
      "end_time": 577950.0,
      "text": "that&#39;ll allow this ASHA worker to become an interesting filter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 577950.0,
      "end_time": 580465.0,
      "text": "but not just a filter, a really well thought through referral"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 580465.0,
      "end_time": 583946.0,
      "text": "system that allows load balancing of the network,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 583946.0,
      "end_time": 587885.0,
      "text": "and directs patients to different sources of health care"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 587885.0,
      "end_time": 591765.0,
      "text": "based on the severity or the criticalness of those situations?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 591765.0,
      "end_time": 593746.0,
      "text": "So the real key question was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 593746.0,
      "end_time": 595414.0,
      "text": "how do we empower this woman?"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 595414.0,
      "end_time": 597341.0,
      "text": "How do we empower her with simple tools"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 597341.0,
      "end_time": 600292.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s not diagnostic but more screening in nature"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 600292.0,
      "end_time": 604720.0,
      "text": "so she at least knows how to advise the patients better?"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 604720.0,
      "end_time": 606100.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;ll make such a huge difference on the system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 606100.0,
      "end_time": 611180.0,
      "text": "because the amount of waiting time and the amount of"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 611180.0,
      "end_time": 612938.0,
      "text": "distances that people need to travel, often sometimes"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 612938.0,
      "end_time": 615611.0,
      "text": "seven to 15 kilometers, sometimes by foot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 615611.0,
      "end_time": 621740.0,
      "text": "to get a simple health check done, is very, very detrimental"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 621740.0,
      "end_time": 623527.0,
      "text": "in the sense that it really dissuades people"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 623528.0,
      "end_time": 625537.0,
      "text": "from getting access to health care."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 625537.0,
      "end_time": 627572.0,
      "text": "So if there was something that she could do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 627572.0,
      "end_time": 628681.0,
      "text": "that would be amazing."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 628681.0,
      "end_time": 631742.0,
      "text": "So what we did was that we converted this device"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 631742.0,
      "end_time": 633559.0,
      "text": "into a medical device."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 633559.0,
      "end_time": 634834.0,
      "text": "I want to demo this actually,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 634835.0,
      "end_time": 637508.0,
      "text": "because it&#39;s a very simple process."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 637508.0,
      "end_time": 639917.0,
      "text": "Bruno, do you want to join us? (Cheers)"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 639917.0,
      "end_time": 646119.0,
      "text": "Come along. (Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 646119.0,
      "end_time": 649440.0,
      "text": "So, what we&#39;re going to do is that"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 649440.0,
      "end_time": 652160.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re going to measure a few basic parameters on you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 652160.0,
      "end_time": 654871.0,
      "text": "including your pulse rate and the amount of oxygen"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 654871.0,
      "end_time": 656744.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s there in your blood."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 656744.0,
      "end_time": 660350.0,
      "text": "So you&#39;re going to put your thumb on top of this."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 660350.0,
      "end_time": 661809.0,
      "text": "Bruno Giussani: Like this, works?"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 661809.0,
      "end_time": 663475.0,
      "text": "Vinay Venkatraman: Yeah. That&#39;s right. BG: Okay."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 663475.0,
      "end_time": 667483.0,
      "text": "VV: So I&#39;m going to start it up. I hope it works."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 667483.0,
      "end_time": 671833.0,
      "text": "(Beeps) It even beeps, because it&#39;s an alarm clock, after all."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 671833.0,
      "end_time": 673844.0,
      "text": "So ... (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 673845.0,
      "end_time": 678236.0,
      "text": "So I take it into the start position, and then"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 678236.0,
      "end_time": 681848.0,
      "text": "I press the read button. (Beeps)"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 681848.0,
      "end_time": 687329.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s taking a little reading from you. (Beeps)"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 687329.0,
      "end_time": 690107.0,
      "text": "And then the pointer goes and points to three different options."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 690107.0,
      "end_time": 693382.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s see what happens here."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 693382.0,
      "end_time": 695464.0,
      "text": "(Beeps) Oh Bruno, you can go home, actually."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 695465.0,
      "end_time": 699301.0,
      "text": "BG: Great. Good news. (Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 699301.0,
      "end_time": 701646.0,
      "text": "VV: So ... (Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 701646.0,
      "end_time": 704863.0,
      "text": "So the thing about this is that"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 704863.0,
      "end_time": 708968.0,
      "text": "if the pointer, unfortunately, had pointed to the red spot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 708968.0,
      "end_time": 710814.0,
      "text": "we would have to rush you to a hospital."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 710814.0,
      "end_time": 714934.0,
      "text": "Luckily, not today. And if it had pointed to the orange"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 714934.0,
      "end_time": 717762.0,
      "text": "or the amber, it basically meant you had to have,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 717763.0,
      "end_time": 720807.0,
      "text": "sort of, more continuous care from the health care worker."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 720807.0,
      "end_time": 723158.0,
      "text": "So that was a very simple three-step screening process"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 723158.0,
      "end_time": 725273.0,
      "text": "that could basically change the equation"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 725273.0,
      "end_time": 728130.0,
      "text": "of how public health care works in so many different ways."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 728130.0,
      "end_time": 729910.0,
      "text": "BG: Thank you for the good news. VV: Yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 729910.0,
      "end_time": 734303.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 734303.0,
      "end_time": 737743.0,
      "text": "So, very briefly, I&#39;ll just explain to you how this is done,"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 737743.0,
      "end_time": 740330.0,
      "text": "because that&#39;s the more interesting part."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 740330.0,
      "end_time": 742727.0,
      "text": "So essentially, the three things that are required"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 742727.0,
      "end_time": 747255.0,
      "text": "to make this conversion from this guy to this guy"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 747255.0,
      "end_time": 751384.0,
      "text": "is a cheap remote control for a television"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 751384.0,
      "end_time": 754295.0,
      "text": "that you can almost find in every home today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 754295.0,
      "end_time": 758900.0,
      "text": "some parts from a computer mouse, basically,"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 758900.0,
      "end_time": 761872.0,
      "text": "something that you can scavenge for very low cost,"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 761872.0,
      "end_time": 764782.0,
      "text": "and a few parts that have to be pre-programmed."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 764783.0,
      "end_time": 767184.0,
      "text": "Basically this is a micro-controller with a few"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 767184.0,
      "end_time": 769978.0,
      "text": "extra components that can be shipped for very little cost"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 769979.0,
      "end_time": 772972.0,
      "text": "across the world, and that&#39;s what is all required"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 772972.0,
      "end_time": 775363.0,
      "text": "with a little bit of local tinkering talent"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 775363.0,
      "end_time": 778150.0,
      "text": "to convert the device into something else."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 778150.0,
      "end_time": 781545.0,
      "text": "So we are right now doing some systematic field tests"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 781546.0,
      "end_time": 784596.0,
      "text": "to basically ascertain whether something like this actually"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 784596.0,
      "end_time": 786163.0,
      "text": "makes sense to the ASHA worker."
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 786163.0,
      "end_time": 789707.0,
      "text": "We are going through some reference tests to compare it"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 789707.0,
      "end_time": 793165.0,
      "text": "against professional equipment to see if there&#39;s a degree"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 793165.0,
      "end_time": 795487.0,
      "text": "of change in efficacy and if it actually makes an impact"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 795487.0,
      "end_time": 798940.0,
      "text": "in people&#39;s lives. But most importantly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 798950.0,
      "end_time": 799890.0,
      "text": "what we are trying to do right now"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 799890.0,
      "end_time": 802144.0,
      "text": "is we are trying to scale this up, because there"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 802144.0,
      "end_time": 804831.0,
      "text": "are over 250,000 ASHA workers on the ground"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 804831.0,
      "end_time": 807568.0,
      "text": "who are these amazing foot soldiers, and if we can"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 807568.0,
      "end_time": 811127.0,
      "text": "give at least a fraction of them the access to these things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 811128.0,
      "end_time": 814860.0,
      "text": "it just changes the way the economics of public health care"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 814860.0,
      "end_time": 817970.0,
      "text": "works, and it changes the way systems actually function,"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 817970.0,
      "end_time": 821363.0,
      "text": "not just on a systematic planning level,"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 821363.0,
      "end_time": 824548.0,
      "text": "but also in a very grassroots, bottom-up level."
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 824548.0,
      "end_time": 827349.0,
      "text": "So that&#39;s it, and we hope to do this in a big way."
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 827349.0,
      "end_time": 830507.0,
      "text": "Thank you. (Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 830507.0,
      "end_time": 839152.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}